title.narrative:
•	Number of advances or defences that focus on or affect a specific vulnerable population are achieved in legislation/policy;
•	Level and impact of media attention on the special vulnerability of children/women/migrants/ or minorities to torture and ill treatment in the national and/or international media.
•	Steps taken in priority countries towards greater accountability for abuses, such as indictments or legal judgments sanctioning abuse.

target.value:
•	At least two (2) advances or defences that focus on or affect a specific vulnerable population are achieved in legislation/policy (each year);
•	At least five (5) high-impact pieces of media attention on the special vulnerability of children/women/migrants/minorities to torture and ill treatment achieved in national and/or international media (each year);
•	At least one (1) step is taken in focus countries towards greater accountability for abuses. such as indictments or legal judgments sanctioning abuse (each year).

•	At least two (2) advances or defences that focus on or affect a specific vulnerable population are achieved in legislation/policy (each year);
•	At least five (5) high-impact pieces of media attention on the special vulnerability of children/women/migrants/minorities to torture and ill treatment achieved in national and/or international media (each year);
•	At least one (1) step is taken in focus countries towards greater accountability for abuses. such as indictments or legal judgments sanctioning abuse (each year).
